{"talk":{"id":36063,"name":"Muhammed Idris: What refugees need to start new lives","description":"Every minute, 20 people are newly displaced by climate change, economic crisis and political instability, according to the UNHCR. How can we help them overcome the barriers to starting new lives? TED Resident Muhammed Idris is leading a team of technologists, researchers and refugees to develop Atar, the first-ever AI-powered virtual advocate that guides displaced people through resettlement, helping restore their rights and dignity. \"Getting access to the right resources and information can be the difference between life and death,\" Idris says.","slug":"muhammed_idris_what_refugees_need_to_start_new_lives","recorded_at":"2018-12-05 00:00:00","published_at":"2019-04-04 14:51:39","updated_at":"2020-09-28 21:42:15","viewed_count":0,"emailed_count":0,"event":{"id":434,"name":"TED Residency"},"images":[{"image":{"size":"113x85","url":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/b12e1fd04b0dcc83812d95584fab82b1daae3e84_113x85.jpg"}},{"image":{"size":"240x180","url":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/b12e1fd04b0dcc83812d95584fab82b1daae3e84_240x180.jpg"}},{"image":{"size":"615x461","url":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/b12e1fd04b0dcc83812d95584fab82b1daae3e84_615x461.jpg"}},{"image":{"size":"2400x1800","url":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/b12e1fd04b0dcc83812d95584fab82b1daae3e84_2400x1800.jpg"}}],"image_16x9":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/ca6dc0c7fec4ace7188b6c41a73be363f43a5175_2880x1620.jpg","media":{"internal":{"64k":{"uri":"https:\/\/download.ted.com\/talks\/MuhammedIdris_2018S-64k.mp4?apikey=c692baa7dafbf74e4fbde1ac88b44cafc96cfe7a","filesize_bytes":3057956,"mime_type":"video\/mp4"},"180k":{"uri":"https:\/\/download.ted.com\/talks\/MuhammedIdris_2018S-180k.mp4?apikey=c692baa7dafbf74e4fbde1ac88b44cafc96cfe7a","filesize_bytes":8433431,"mime_type":"video\/mp4"},"320k":{"uri":"https:\/\/download.ted.com\/talks\/MuhammedIdris_2018S-320k.mp4?apikey=c692